Package: slbrand
Title: Shelby Level Brand Theme for Shiny and Quarto
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Shelby", "Level", email = "you@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Centralizes the Shelby Level brand.yml file, logo assets, and
    helper functions so brand-consistent theming (colors, typography, and
    custom CSS rules) can be applied across multiple Shiny dashboards and
    Quarto documents from a single source of truth.
